comments: Simmons (PHI) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Lamb (CHA) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Lamb (CHA) briefly places his hands on Ennis' (PHI) back but immediately slides them off.
Ennis III (PHI) establishes a legal picking position by firming up and absorbing the contact from Lamb (CHA).
Kaminsky (CHA) gives Butler (PHI) room to land as Butler extends his foot forward on the shot attempt.
Ennis III (PHI) makes contact to the body of Lamb (CHA) during his shooting motion that affects his driving shot attempt.
Batum (CHA) makes brief contact with Butler (PHI) on the perimeter, but disengages when he slides his hands off.
Redick (PHI) maintains a legal pivot foot.
Walker (CHA) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Redick (PHI).
RLS shows Williams (CHA) takes an unnatural path in transition by seeking out contact with Simmons (PHI) when he runs into him and dislodges him from his position.
Redick (PHI) establishes himself in a legal picking position in the path of Batum (CHA) and absorbs the contact from Batum.
Walker (CHA) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Butler (PHI).
Harris (PHI) briefly places both hands on Bacon's (CHA) back but the contact is marginal as he releases for the long rebound.
Lamb (CHA) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Ennis III (PHI).
Butler (PHI) makes marginal contact with Walker's (CHA) arm, but Walker is still able to play through the contact and attempt his pass.
Ennis III (PHI) makes contact to the body of Lamb (CHA) during his shooting motion that affects his jump shot attempt.
Batum (CHA) commits a take foul on Butler (PHI).
Biyombo (CHA) commits a take foul on Harris (PHI).
McConnell (PHI) legally moves alongside of Lamb (CHA) and absorbs the contact from Lamb during the driving shot attempt.  McConnell avoids making contact with Lamb's arm when he swipes down.
Harris (PHI) and Batum (CHA) engage and disengage during the rebound attempt.
RLB shows Harris (PHI) makes incidental contact with Batum's (CHA) arm after the ball has been released from his hand during the tip-in attempt.
Kaminsky (CHA) commits a take foul on Harris (PHI).
